2,1,beat_00_opening_frame,"Before we go further, you need to know something. It made sense. The sentence \'97 \{core_sentence\} \'97 made sense. Not it was understandable. Not you were doing your best. It made sense. It was adaptive. It kept you safe. Let me show you when."\
