  That''s what it cost you.\
\
  '\
fighting_yourself_explanation: 'The emptiness isn''t going away. That''s not the goal.\
\
  The goal is to stop fighting yourself for having it.\
\
  '\
uncertainty_as_condition_description: 'The emptiness isn''t going away. That''s not\
  the goal.\
\
  The goal is to stop fighting yourself for having it.\
\
  '\
uncertainty_is_condition_statement: 'Uncertainty isn''t going away. That''s not the\
  goal.\
\
  The goal is to stop fighting yourself for having it.\
\
  '\
weather_metaphor: 'You don''t fight the weather. You don''t fight gravity.\
\
  You don''t fight the emptiness. You move with it.\
\
  '\
weather_metaphor_explanation: 'You don''t fight the weather. You don''t fight gravity.\
\
  You don''t fight the emptiness. You move with it.\
\
  '\
stop_fighting_reframe: 'All that energy you spent fighting?\
\
  That''s yours now. To use while empty.\
\
  '\
nothing_to_fight_statement: 'There''s nothing to fight.\
\
  '\
energy_reclamation_description: 'All that energy you spent fighting?\
\
  That''s yours now. To use while empty.\
\
  '\
