# PART 3: PERSONA SCENE COVERAGE\
\
## How Many Scenes Per Persona?\
\
### Minimum Viable Coverage\
**12 scenes** \'97 one per socket, fully authored\
\
This is the baseline. Every persona \'d7 topic combination requires 12 unique scenes.\
\
### Why Not Fewer?\
Reusing scenes across personas destroys the architecture's purpose. If Gen Z and Millennial share 
\f9\fs28 \cb11 scene_01
\f0\fs32 \cb7 , the personalization is fake.\
\
### Why Not More?\
Scene density is capped. More than 12 scenes per book creates exhaustion and dilutes authorial voice.\
\
